<inglise> The laws, regulations and administrative provisions shall be applied so as to: </inglise>
<eesti> &Otilde;igus- ja haldusnorme kohaldatakse nii, et see v&otilde;imaldaks: </eesti>
<inglise> - authorise the marketing of the products defined in the Annex if they conform to the definitions and rules laid down in this Directive, with effect from 13 September 2000, </inglise>
<eesti> - alates 13. septembrist 2000 lubada lisas m&auml;&auml;ratletud toodete m&uuml;&uuml;ki, kui need vastavad k&auml;esolevas direktiivis s&auml;testatud m&auml;&auml;ratlustele ja eeskirjadele; </eesti>
<inglise> - prohibit the marketing of products which fail to conform to this Directive, with effect from 13 September 2001. </inglise>
